---
import site from "../site.config.json";
import ACForm from "../components/ACForm.astro";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Medical Transcription Australia | Dictation Solutions Australia</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Medical transcription options for Australian healthcare. Traditional transcription, Dragon speech recognition, and AI-assisted workflows. Compare approaches for your practice." />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://dictationsolutions.com.au/medical-transcription" />
    <style is:inline>
      *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box}
      body{margin:0;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;background:#fff;color:#0f1a10}
      a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
      .wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}
      .page-header{background:#1c2b1e;color:white;padding:48px 0 40px}
      .breadcrumb{font-size:13px;color:#86a989;margin-bottom:16px}
      .breadcrumb a{color:#86a989}
      h1{font-size:38px;line-height:1.15;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.02em}
      .lead{font-size:17px;color:#b8cbb9;margin:0;max-width:600px}
      .content{padding:56px 0}
      .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(12,1fr);gap:24px}
      .c8{grid-column:span 8}.c4{grid-column:span 4}.c6{grid-column:span 6}
      h2{font-size:26px;margin:0 0 12px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#1c2b1e}
      p{color:#4a5e4d;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 16px}
      .approach-card{background:#f4f6f4;border:1px solid #d4e0d6;border-radius:16px;padding:24px}
      .approach-card h3{font-size:18px;margin:0 0 8px;color:#1c2b1e}
      .tag{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:12px;text-transform:uppercase}
      .tag-traditional{background:#e8ede8;color:#1c2b1e}
      .tag-modern{background:#2d7a3a;color:white}
      .tag-cloud{background:#1c4b8a;color:white}
      footer{background:#111;color:#64748b;padding:28px 0;font-size:14px}
      .footer-inner{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
      @media(max-width:900px){.c8,.c4,.c6{grid-column:span 12}h1{font-size:28px}}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page-header">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Dictation Solutions Australia</a> &rsaquo; Medical Transcription</div>
        <h1>Medical Transcription Australia</h1>
        <p class="lead">Traditional transcription, speech recognition, and AI-assisted workflows for Australian healthcare. Understand your options and choose what suits your practice.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="c8">
            <h2>How medical transcription has changed</h2>
            <p>Medical transcription - converting a clinician's dictated notes into structured clinical documentation - has evolved significantly. The traditional model (dictate to a recorder, send to a transcriptionist) is still used but increasingly replaced by speech recognition and AI-assisted documentation tools.</p>
            <h2 style="margin-top:40px">Four approaches to medical documentation</h2>
            <div class="grid" style="margin-top:16px">
              <div class="c6"><div class="approach-card"><span class="tag tag-traditional">Traditional</span><h3>Dictation and manual transcription</h3><p>Clinician dictates to a digital recorder. Audio sent to a human transcriptionist. Accurate but slower and more expensive per document.</p><p style="font-size:14px;color:#4a5e4d">Suits: specialists with complex dictation, practices with existing workflows</p></div></div>
              <div class="c6"><div class="approach-card"><span class="tag tag-modern">Recommended</span><h3>Dragon Medical One</h3><p>Clinician speaks directly into their clinical system. Speech recognised in real time. Cloud-based with built-in medical vocabulary for 100+ specialties.</p><p style="font-size:14px;color:#4a5e4d">Suits: GPs, specialists wanting to reduce transcription costs and turnaround time</p><a href="/dragon-medical-one" style="color:#2d7a3a;font-weight:600;font-size:14px">Learn about Dragon Medical One</a></div></div>
              <div class="c6"><div class="approach-card"><span class="tag tag-cloud">AI</span><h3>AI-assisted documentation</h3><p>Ambient AI tools that listen to the clinical conversation and generate structured notes. Emerging category. [VERIFY current Australian availability]</p><p style="font-size:14px;color:#4a5e4d">Suits: high-volume consultation environments open to emerging technology</p></div></div>
              <div class="c6"><div class="approach-card"><span class="tag tag-traditional">Cloud</span><h3>Cloud transcription services</h3><p>Audio files uploaded to a cloud platform for automated transcription. Lower cost than human transcription. Medical-grade accuracy requires specialist platforms.</p><p style="font-size:14px;color:#4a5e4d">Suits: allied health, administrative documentation, general professional use</p><a href="https://www.speechrecognition.cloud" style="color:#2d7a3a;font-weight:600;font-size:14px">SpeechRecognition Cloud</a></div></div>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top:40px">For current pricing and a demonstration of Dragon Medical One, contact <a href="https://www.voicerecognition.com.au" style="color:#2d7a3a;font-weight:600">Voice Recognition Australia</a>, authorised Australian reseller.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="c4"><ACForm /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <footer><div class="wrap"><div class="footer-inner"><div>&copy; {year} {site.siteName}</div><div style="display:flex;gap:20px"><a href="/">Home</a><a href="/privacy">Privacy</a><a href="/terms">Terms</a></div></div></div></footer>
  </body>
</html>
